  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK598">
<l>uḷḷa milātava reytā rulakattu </l>
<l> vaḷḷiya meṉṉuñ cerukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have no (greatness of) mind, will not acquire the joy of saying in the world, "we have excercised liaberality".</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
